                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6089" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0927</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8242 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">勿道金融守旧规，鸿鹄改革任先锋——新金融工具准则对A农商银行信贷业务的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Don’t Follow the Old Financial Rules, Honghu is the Pioneer of Reform ——The impact of new financial instrument standards on the credit business of A rural commercial bank</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">魏明，张新华，苗悦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西省农村信用社联合社</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农商银行；新金融工具准则；信贷业务；预期信用损失模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rural commercial bank; New financial instrument standards; Credit business; Expected credit loss model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2008年全球金融动荡的影响至今还未完全消散，国际会计准则理事会为进一步提高会计质量，修订金融工具准则。2014年，国际会计准则理事会发布《国际财务报告准则第9号—金融工具》（IFRS9）。为保持和国际会计准则的趋同，2017年，我国财政部发布了关于印发修订《企业会计准则第22号--金融工具确认和计量》的通知财会【2017】7号，主要是对金融资产进行重分类并使用预期信用损失模型计提减值准备，非上市企业从2021年1月1日起实施新准则。本案例根据A农商银行的现阶段发展情况，对2020年前三季度的报表项目进行分析以便新准则变革平稳落地，针对核心的信贷业务如何更好地应对新准则的变化进行探讨，对地方性金融机构的准则变革提供一定的借鉴思路。本案例有助于学员掌握新金融工具准则内的金融资产变化，启发学员优化新金融工具准则的应对方案以及分析思考能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The impact of the global financial turmoil in 2008 has not yet fully dissipated, and the IASB revised its standards on financial instruments to further improve the quality of accounting. in 2014, the IASB issued International Financial Reporting Standard 9 - Financial Instruments (IFRS 9). In order to maintain convergence with international accounting standards, in 2017, China&#39;s Ministry of Finance issued a circular on the issuance of amendments to AS 22 - Recognition and Measurement of Financial Instruments Caihui [2017] No. 7, which focuses on the reclassification of financial assets and the use of an expected credit loss model to provide for impairment, with non-listed enterprises implementing the new standard from January 1 2021. This case is based on the current development of Agricultural and Commercial Bank A. The case analyses the reporting items for the first three quarters of 2020 in order to facilitate the smooth implementation of the new standard changes, and discusses how the core credit business can better cope with the changes of the new standard, providing some reference ideas for the standard changes of local financial institutions. This case helps participants to grasp the changes in financial assets within the new financial instruments standard, inspires them to optimise their response to the new financial instruments standard and enhances their analytical thinking skills.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新金融工具准则</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
